I really got the feeling she was bringing up a murder that hadn't actually occurred until she said so, as a defense mechanism.
附加记录：    

Well someone gets a cookie!

Or at least, that is my personal interpretation of how the entity's abilities work. When it comes to skips that appear to play fast and loose with the conventional laws of reality, I tend to think it's best to leave a healthy amount of ambiguity and to let readers come up with their own interpretations of exactly what's . That's why I left the tests in a pending state rather than categorically explaining how its abilities actually worked.







